    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I had a look at that. It doesn't fit with what we are looking for.  What we were looking for is find objects within X km using a range slider of IP at the start and eventually using the browser geolocation library for mobile devices. \n\nAfter having a look the main items that need to be moved to cross platform allow dev on windows is build.sh and dev.sh files are the ones that look fairly easy to move to either JS or .bat for Windows.\n",
